thread.title: James Thomas
thread.title_full: Slater and Gordon Lawyers reviewed by James Thomas

author: James Thomas
title: James Thomas
text: Monique Oysten @ Campbelltown branch was awesome. She stayed in contact always, was on top of the game when some of the solicitors were leaving (2 left during the case) and she was an integral player in our case going through smoothly. It would not have done so if not for her extraordinary, and massive efforts. Joel redman was pretty good too, although he was only there near the end. 5stars.
